
User & Server

1) User-->Server
	login/logoff
	*status

2) Server---> User
	*online/offline
	
3) User ---> User

	direct msg to users
	msg <user> <text>
	
	ie. msg temp hello world  - ---< sent 
	
	temp: msg guest hello world ------received
	
	broadcast msg to all user
	
	//group messaging/ # topic 
	send msg to topic . every member of topic will recieve msg
	
	# topic - chat room / or / group chat 
	join topic				-> command to join topic 
	msg #topic body			--> command to send msg to group
	
	
	
Commands : 
	login <username> <password>
	loggoff